{
  "texts": [
    "We selected 18 sequences each from ASR, GAN and ESM-MSA.",
    "Only 13 natural test sequences were selected, because we had already screened 5 similar natural sequences in the remediation for round 1.",
    "Natural test sequences were selected using the same criteria as used for model-generated sequences.",
    "The number of expressed enzymes with activity above the background was substantially higher than that in round 1, with 66% of natural controls showing activity when expressed in E. coli, and at least 50% of generated sequences were active for every model-enzyme family combination except for GAN-MDH, where only 2 of 18 sequences were active (Extended Data Table 1 and Supplementary Figs. 13-16).",
